    <h2 class="text-light mb-4">🆘 Help & Support</h2>
    <div class="card bg-dark text-white p-4">
        <h4>Welcome to the Online Music Store Help Center!</h4>
        <p>Here are some quick tips to get you started:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🎧 Browse music by genre or use the search bar to find your favorite songs.</li>
